  It now also records the Step-4 dynamic screen: under that fixed package the
  hybrid is dynamically weak, and direction-field diffusion demands stronger
  control than the inherited bounds provide.
  It also records the Step-4 stop condition: if the fixed-package audits leave
  every candidate dynamically weak or static-only, the branch should halt
  before kernel-level representation work.
- `exact-rewrite-architecture-screening/`: reusable notes on fixing the
